            Prospective Students
          Heading link



 
Copy link



            LAS houses 25 departments and serves more than 10,000 students.  We offer a unique learning environment that combines well-respected academic programs and faculty with innovative research opportunities and easy access to Chicago’s rich urban setting.
          





